{"tid":289314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"離任前訪問　蘇錦樑：個人撐發三免費電視牌　已盡量向行會表達意見","createTime":"2017-06-19T01:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T01:26:58.000Z","uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6139cc95f46beb62b57e94b025e9fffdfd7951b","tid":289314,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"即將離任的商務及經濟發展局局長蘇錦樑接受多個傳媒訪問，他提到，自己支持發3個牌照，即包括向港視發牌，已盡量在行會表達意見。但他認為，發牌過程依足廣播政策和相關程序，上訴法庭判政府勝訴，反映政府沒違規，而且社會已看到電視市場營運困難、競爭大，「行會是有行會智慧」。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，自己支持發3個牌照，「我盡量在行會表達我的意見，最終決定不能發出全部3個牌照，我的職份是要根據政府提供的資料對外解釋&hellip;那段時間，要頂住別人的攻擊，那是我的承擔。」<br />\n<br />\n蘇錦樑又形容，這是他最逆境時刻，因該次哽咽被指是做戲，他感到很遺憾，因他當時是擔心港視300多人的就業情況才哽咽，「我哽咽因為我的決定會影響到別人就業。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%9B%A2%E4%BB%BB%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E8%98%87%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%91-%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%90%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%89%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%89%8C-%E5%B7%B2%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%90%91%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E8%2598%2587%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%25A8%2591-%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2592%2590%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2589%258C-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B%2F&d=qCyVfIZAWkoOQgf583wEdv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1262d3a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E5%2595%258F-%25E8%2598%2587%25E9%258C%25A6%25E6%25A8%2591-%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2592%2590%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2585%258D%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2589%258C-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2590%2591%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25A6%258B%2F&h=05cf4bdb\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E9%9B%A2%E4%BB%BB%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F-%E8%98%87%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%91-%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%92%90%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%89%E5%85%8D%E8%B2%BB%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%89%8C-%E5%B7%B2%E7%9B%A1%E9%87%8F%E5%90%91%E8%A1%8C%E6%9C%83%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B/</a>"}]}